name blindtext
category Package
revision 77682
shortdesc Producing 'blind' text for testing
longdesc The package provides the commands \blindtext and \Blindtext for
longdesc creating 'blind' text useful in testing new classes and
longdesc packages, and \blinddocument, \Blinddocument for creating an
longdesc entire random document with sections, lists, mathematics, etc.
longdesc The package supports three languages, english, (n)german and
longdesc latin; the latin option provides a short "lorem ipsum" (for a
longdesc fuller lorem ipsum text, see the lipsum package).
